snippet.title: Opeth - Pale Communion Full Album
snippet.description:
Promotional only. All rights to WMG, Warner Music Group, Roadrunner Records. All music by Opeth.

That's it bitches, the entire discography. Assuming I don't get the banhammer in a month's time. I hope to continue to provide you all with some kickass music. This album reminds me of a less technical Winds and a less random Ulver. 

• Eternal Rains Will Come 0:00
• Cusp Of Eternity 6:45
• Moon Above, Sun Below 12:19
• Elysian Woes 23:13
• Goblin 28:01
• River 32:36
• Voice Of Treason 40:09
• Faith In Others 47:50
• Solitude (Live) 55:52
